#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text038"
msgid ""
"To know Calamity Ganon's true form, one must\n"
"know the story from an age long past. <1.ra>The demon king was born into "
"this kingdom, but his\n"
"transformation into Malice created the horror you\n"
"see now."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text039"
msgid ""
"Stories of Ganon were passed from generation to\n"
"generation in the form of legends and fairy tales.<1.ra>But there was "
"also...a prophecy."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text040"
msgid ""
"\"The signs of a resurrection of\n"
"Calamity Ganon are clear. <1.ra>And the power to oppose it lies\n"
"dormant beneath the ground.\""
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text042"
msgid ""
"These relics, the Divine Beasts, were giant machines\n"
"piloted by warriors.<1.ra>We also found the Guardians, an army of "
"mechanical\n"
"soldiers who fought autonomously."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text046"
msgid ""
"The princess, her appointed knight, and the rest\n"
"of the Champions were on the brink of sealing\n"
"away Ganon..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text047"
msgid ""
"But nay...<1.ra>Ganon was cunning, and he responded with a plan\n"
"beyond our imagining."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text048"
msgid ""
"He appeared from deep below Hyrule Castle,\n"
"seized control of the Guardians and the\n"
"Divine Beasts,<1.ra>and turned them against us."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text049"
msgid ""
"The Champions lost their lives. Those residing in the\n"
"castle as well.<1.ra>The appointed knight, gravely wounded, collapsed\n"
"while defending the princess..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text050"
msgid ""
"And thus, the kingdom of Hyrule was devastated\n"
"absolutely by Calamity Ganon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text051"
msgid "However..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text052"
msgid "The princess survived...<1.ra>to face Ganon alone."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text053"
msgid ""
"Link...<1.ra>You are our final hope. <2.ra>The fate of Hyrule rests with "
"you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text054"
msgid ""
"This coincided with ancient legends, oft repeated\n"
"throughout our land."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text055"
msgid ""
"We also learned of a princess with a sacred power\n"
"and her appointed knight, chosen by the sword that\n"
"seals the darkness. <1.ra>It was they who sealed Ganon away using the "
"power\n"
"of these ancient relics."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text056"
msgid ""
"One hundred years ago, there was a princess\n"
"set to inherit a sacred power and a skilled knight\n"
"at her side.<1.ra>It was clear that we must follow our ancestors' path."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text057"
msgid ""
"We decided to heed the prophecy and began\n"
"excavating large areas of land. <1.ra>It wasn't long before we discovered"
" several ancient\n"
"relics made by the hands of our distant ancestors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text065"
msgid ""
"We selected four skilled individuals from across\n"
"Hyrule and tasked them with the duty of piloting the\n"
"Divine Beasts."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Demo101_0_Text066"
msgid ""
"With the princess as their commander, we dubbed\n"
"these pilots Championsâ€”<1.ra>a name that would solidify their unique bond."
msgstr ""

